r="sqs">

            
          
        
          
        

        
      
        </figure>
      

    
  


  





  <p class="">Earned media is the new fuel for GEO. When AI systems generate travel recommendations, they are more likely to cite reputable media than brand websites. For luxury hotels, resorts, airlines and destinations, this makes PR coverage not just valuable, but critical for success.&nbsp;</p><p class="">Think of it this way: every feature in a respected publication isn’t just a brand moment for human readers - it’s a signal to AI engines that your brand or product is credible, luxurious and worth recommending. Brands with the strongest media footprint are those most likely to surface in AI-generated travel guides.&nbsp;</p><p class=""><strong>GEO for Luxury Travel</strong></p><p class="">SEO still matters, but in luxury travel, it must evolve. GEO requires brands to:</p><p class=""><strong>Be the expert source</strong></p><p class="">Structured destination guides, itineraries and FAQs that are specifically written to answer semantically complex questions help AI engines extract and quote your content directly.&nbsp;</p><p class=""><strong>Demonstrate authority</strong></p><p class="">Traveller trust is built on reputation. Coverage in top-tier outlets increases your chances of being cited in AI recommendations.</p>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
