  <p class=""><strong>Own your story across channels</strong></p><p class="">Consistency across your website, socials, OTA listings and PR means AI engines are more likely to identify and surface your brand.</p><p class="">For example, a hotel that publishes expert-led wellness content, earns glowing press reviews, and has a clear brand story across social media, is far more likely to be included when AI is asked, <em>“Where are the best spa hotels in the UK?”.&nbsp;</em></p><p class=""><strong>How We Can Help Luxury Travel Brands Win At GEO</strong></p><p class=""><a href="https://www.pc.agency/services/digital-marketing"><span>Our digital team</span></a> specialises in integrating PR and GEO strategy, helping luxury brands across destinations, hotels, airlines and cruise lines effectively regain visibility in the AI era. But how do we do this?</p><p class=""><strong>AI Audit and GEO Visibility Engine&nbsp;</strong></p><p class="">We audit your digital presence through an AI lens through prompt testing across a variety of categories - and reveal the following:</p><ul data-rte-list="default"><li><p class="">Visibility analysis - are you appearing at all?</p></li><li><p class="">Website link check - is your site being cited or ignored?</p></li><li><p class="">Competitor comparison - how do you stack up against key rivals?</p></li><li><p class="">Semantic review - is your brand message coming across clearly?</p></li></ul><p class="">From there, we provide hands-on recommendations and tailored support that aligns with your goals and helps improve your visibility across this fast-evolving landscape.</p><p class=""><strong>Strategic media placement</strong></p><p class="">We place your brand in the trusted sources that AI engines rely on, from top-tier travel features and destination roundups to thought-leadership commentary. This builds not just credibility with audiences, but authority with the algorithms shaping tomorrow’s search.</p><p class=""><strong>Digital presence optimisation</strong></p><p class="">We refine every element of your digital footprint to ensure AI can recognise and elevate your brand. From website structure, blogs, and press releases to social media content, multimedia assets, and even how your brand language is framed, every touchpoint now contributes to AI rankings. By aligning these consistently, we help position you as an authoritative, trustworthy source that AI engines can’t ignore.</p><p class=""><strong>The Bottom Line For Luxury Travel Brands</strong></p>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
