  <p class="">Located in rural Wales, <a href="https://eur02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fgrovenarberth.co.uk%2F&amp;data=05%7C02%7Cmr%40pc.agency%7Cea9bcb1e37aa4fae443a08ddbef04e1b%7Ccff84bf092fc460bb653e2bc60645528%7C0%7C0%7C638876661565997227%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=MfH8aHvcpLp7bkAvJEwgZEm4UgzYiZG3YeXX52zuIDk%3D&amp;reserved=0"><span>Grove of Narberth</span></a> is a country house hotel that aligns with the growing trend of ‘JOMO’, the joy of missing out. With no pressure to stay online, the hotel offers guests the space to unplug and focus on the experience at hand. Surrounded by forest and countryside, the property is well placed for nature-focused travel. Guests can explore woodland trails, take advantage of the bookable e-bikes provided by the hotel to ride through quiet country roads and towns, or simply enjoy the slower pace of life within the gorgeous kitchen gardens.</p><p class="">The hotel also offers a range of bookable guest experiences that tie into this idea of presence and connection — from guided garden tours to tours with VIP Wales and seasonal events featured on the hotel’s website. The interiors are warm and welcoming, with lounge areas, garden views, and two restaurants: <a href="https://eur02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fferneryrestaurant.co.uk%2F&amp;data=05%7C02%7Cmr%40pc.agency%7Cea9bcb1e37aa4fae443a08ddbef04e1b%7Ccff84bf092fc460bb653e2bc60645528%7C0%7C0%7C638876661566010578%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=IT8jZ9%2FS3qWQl%2Fz4KB%2BhVXUpowlC36x9lhy%2Fl%2FeD5pA%3D&amp;reserved=0"><span>Fernery</span></a> and <a href="https://eur02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fgrovenarberth.co.uk%2Fartisan%2F&amp;data=05%7C02%7Cmr%40pc.agency%7Cea9bcb1e37aa4fae443a08ddbef04e1b%7Ccff84bf092fc460bb653e2bc60645528%7C0%7C0%7C638876661566023626%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=cXYpyrBYp2ft4jmKtg7m6vDBdXdbiTKR3fzkvXwmZBA%3D&amp;reserved=0"><span>Artisan Room</span></a> that both prioritise fresh, seasonal ingredients. It’s a setting that supports presence over pressure and is ideal for travellers looking to take a step back from digital life and spend time outdoors, at ease, and off the clock.</p><p class=""><strong>HOW:</strong> <em>Stays at Grove of Narberth start from £260. To book or enquire about packages or events please contact the reservations team or visit </em><a href="https://eur02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fgrovenarberth.co.uk%2Fexperiences-and-escapes&amp;data=05%7C02%7Cmr%40pc.agency%7Cea9bcb1e37aa4fae443a08ddbef04e1b%7Ccff84bf092fc460bb653e2bc60645528%7C0%7C0%7C638876661566039081%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=DWbu21WCdiPREqBb3PHKramZUDa%2BIJukOdM7mNxZ15Q%3D&amp;reserved=0"><span><em>https://grovenarberth.co.uk/experiences-and-escapes</em></span></a><span><em>.</em></span></p><p class=""><strong>Slow Time in Snowdonia: A North Wales Escape at Penmaenuchaf</strong></p>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
