  <p class="">Antarctica offers one of the most remote and undisturbed environments on the planet and <a href="https://eur02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwhite-desert.com%2F&amp;data=05%7C02%7Cmr%40pc.agency%7Cea9bcb1e37aa4fae443a08ddbef04e1b%7Ccff84bf092fc460bb653e2bc60645528%7C0%7C0%7C638876661566131888%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=u9qFvYQU4L7gBB3PGWdiNtwm5L3EQ84aPkOa7qVgtsM%3D&amp;reserved=0"><span>White Desert’s</span></a> <a href="https://eur02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwhite-desert.com%2Four-camps%2Fwhichaway%2F&amp;data=05%7C02%7Cmr%40pc.agency%7Cea9bcb1e37aa4fae443a08ddbef04e1b%7Ccff84bf092fc460bb653e2bc60645528%7C0%7C0%7C638876661566144903%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=CrFHUlEk9YmrP9%2FNcYR0ykuj1z%2FkyHAjzksthoeuagI%3D&amp;reserved=0"><span>Whichaway Camp</span></a> provides a rare opportunity to experience it in a way that prioritises rest, reflection and disconnection. The newly launched Wellness Dome at Whichaway overlooks a frozen lake and glacier, designed as a quiet space for movement, stillness or solitude. Guests are encouraged to switch off completely - with no phone signal, they are&nbsp; able to engage with the extraordinary natural surroundings, whether through guided hikes, time in the on-site sauna, or quiet observation of the landscape.</p><p class="">For those seeking a higher-spec base, <a href="https://eur02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwhite-desert.com%2Four-camps%2Fecho%2F&amp;data=05%7C02%7Cmr%40pc.agency%7Cea9bcb1e37aa4fae443a08ddbef04e1b%7Ccff84bf092fc460bb653e2bc60645528%7C0%7C0%7C638876661566158210%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=7MWz1Ia3%2B1BX0TgBi0h%2FZf9Xiqm4G8qwZG%2BNMllfMeM%3D&amp;reserved=0"><span>Echo Camp</span></a> is designed for exclusive-use groups of up to 12. With interiors inspired by space exploration and a focus on ultra-luxury, it combines privacy with access to White Desert’s full programme of activities. These include ice climbing, abseiling, skiing, fat biking, and guided visits to Antarctica’s interior, including the South Pole and Emperor Penguin colony at Atka Bay. Both camps operate with strong environmental principles - White Desert has been carbon neutral since 2007 and is currently pioneering the use of sustainable aviation fuel in Antarctica.</p><p class=""><strong><em>HOW: </em></strong><em>Prices start at $71,500 per person for a 6-day tour and includes return flights &amp; transfers from Cape Town to Antarctica, all accommodation, food &amp; beverages and activities around camp.&nbsp;</em></p><p class=""><strong>Escape the Everyday at Prestonfield House</strong></p>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
