  <p class="">Tucked beneath the iconic Arthur’s Seat and set within 20 acres of private parkland, <a href="https://eur02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.prestonfield.com%2F&amp;data=05%7C02%7Cmr%40pc.agency%7Cea9bcb1e37aa4fae443a08ddbef04e1b%7Ccff84bf092fc460bb653e2bc60645528%7C0%7C0%7C638876661566201322%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=%2FfSPIBSwP%2FwWcqLdJZE1aMr1kNMX0bDtnzzBez%2BJHUg%3D&amp;reserved=0"><span>Prestonfield House</span></a> offers a special chance to embrace the pleasure in unplugging from everyday life. This five-star retreat, just minutes from Edinburgh’s city centre, invites guests to switch off from the outside world and reconnect with nature, beauty, and stillness.</p><p class="">Surrounded by manicured gardens, grazing Highland cows, and striking peacocks, Prestonfield House is a place where the pace of life gently slows. Guests can hike the neighbouring Arthur’s Seat for panoramic views of the city, or simply enjoy a leisurely stroll through the estate’s serene grounds. Whether it’s quiet reflection among the greenery or watching the sunset over the city skyline, there’s no need to scroll; everything guests need is right here. Inside, opulence awaits. From individually styled rooms to indulgent dining at the acclaimed <a href="https://eur02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.prestonfield.com%2Feat-and-drink%2Frhubarb-restaurant%2F&amp;data=05%7C02%7Cmr%40pc.agency%7Cea9bcb1e37aa4fae443a08ddbef04e1b%7Ccff84bf092fc460bb653e2bc60645528%7C0%7C0%7C638876661566218641%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=Q2R5dmLPfJnMa9rwq4A1Y0%2FKRJT%2B78rg1pHdUlVIOW0%3D&amp;reserved=0"><span>Rhubarb</span></a> restaurant, or an intimate rendezvous in the luxurious <a href="https://eur02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.prestonfield.com%2Fprivate-dining%2Fsalon-privee%2F&amp;data=05%7C02%7Cmr%40pc.agency%7Cea9bcb1e37aa4fae443a08ddbef04e1b%7Ccff84bf092fc460bb653e2bc60645528%7C0%7C0%7C638876661566231987%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=6v8bzPrflp%2FEDYniZZgxDMnap0eSBOrrxhttqmn47Eo%3D&amp;reserved=0"><span>Salon Priveé</span></a>, the experience is both grand and grounding. At Prestonfield House, switching off feels effortless, and outsiders will be the ones missing out.</p><p class=""><strong>HOW</strong>: <em>Room rates for Prestonfield House start from £375 per room, per night and includes breakfast. For more information, please visit</em><a href="https://eur02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.prestonfield.com%2F&amp;data=05%7C02%7Cmr%40pc.agency%7Cea9bcb1e37aa4fae443a08ddbef04e1b%7Ccff84bf092fc460bb653e2bc60645528%7C0%7C0%7C638876661566245307%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=D3UKiLN7kLcDgvVOSXMpA1l0YXS8dcSRAet3pC17km8%3D&amp;reserved=0"><em> </em></a><a href="https://eur02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.prestonfield.com%2F&amp;data=05%7C02%7Cmr%40pc.agency%7Cea9bcb1e37aa4fae443a08ddbef04e1b%7Ccff84bf092fc460bb653e2bc60645528%7C0%7C0%7C638876661566258377%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=FQbN9yc0L9nAdBDhMjI3PQtGov%2BlVB%2BPozeLkAXHbtI%3D&amp;reserved=0"><span><em>https://www.prestonfield.com/</em></span></a></p><p class=""><strong>Switch Off and Slow Down at Ellenborough Park</strong></p>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
