  <p class=""><a href="https://eur02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fellenboroughpark.com%2F&amp;data=05%7C02%7Cmr%40pc.agency%7Cea9bcb1e37aa4fae443a08ddbef04e1b%7Ccff84bf092fc460bb653e2bc60645528%7C0%7C0%7C638876661566297528%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=XdrKtXMzMtn%2FfviKL0ZLbJ7tfAS2Kp%2FI%2Facr0WSxsiI%3D&amp;reserved=0"><span>Ellenborough Park</span></a> is a secluded luxury retreat where guests can fully embrace the pleasure in taking a pause. This lovingly restored 15th-century manor house combines historical grandeur with contemporary comfort, offering 61 uniquely designed rooms and suites, set within 90 acres of lush grounds, it is the perfect destination to embrace the joys of peace and quiet.</p><p class="">Situated at the gateway to the Cotswold Way, Ellenborough Park invites guests to disconnect from the digital world and reconnect with nature. Whether it’s gentle strolls through wildflower meadows, invigorating hikes up nearby Cleeve Hill, or peaceful moments spent in the serene spa garden, every experience encourages presence and calm. The <a href="https://eur02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fellenboroughpark.com%2Foffer%2Fspa-garden-retreat-package%2F&amp;data=05%7C02%7Cmr%40pc.agency%7Cea9bcb1e37aa4fae443a08ddbef04e1b%7Ccff84bf092fc460bb653e2bc60645528%7C0%7C0%7C638876661566310739%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=5u5YiPoKXiRwnHwvS6pOEfOwcuXOJdZh%2F8jDtABbTSo%3D&amp;reserved=0"><span>Spa Garden Retreat</span></a> is a tranquil haven designed for digital detox, where guests can unwind amid lush greenery, soothing water features, and calming spaces. It offers a perfect sanctuary to relax before or after indulgent treatments in the spa, allowing visitors to fully immerse themselves in stillness and rejuvenation. It also features the newly launched <a href="https://eur02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fellenboroughpark.com%2Foffer%2Fjapanese-head-spa%2F&amp;data=05%7C02%7Cmr%40pc.agency%7Cea9bcb1e37aa4fae443a08ddbef04e1b%7Ccff84bf092fc460bb653e2bc60645528%7C0%7C0%7C638876661566323877%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=RIuH7a8X8Fz7OhtOgVe2XFQIsK5eLaM6W%2BZcclKhf8I%3D&amp;reserved=0"><span>Japanese Head Spa</span></a>, for the ultimate relaxation experience and the chance for guests to truly switch off for an hour.</p><p class=""><strong>HOW:</strong><em> Room rates at Ellenborough Park start from £269 per night for a double room on a B&amp;B basis. For more information, please visit</em><a href="https://eur02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fellenboroughpark.com%2F&amp;data=05%7C02%7Cmr%40pc.agency%7Cea9bcb1e37aa4fae443a08ddbef04e1b%7Ccff84bf092fc460bb653e2bc60645528%7C0%7C0%7C638876661566336617%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=H2ECn2FjER629m%2BFmAP0WFsNZdILaui27Xh0vZiusvU%3D&amp;reserved=0"><em> </em></a><a href="https://eur02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fellenboroughpark.com%2F&amp;data=05%7C02%7Cmr%40pc.agency%7Cea9bcb1e37aa4fae443a08ddbef04e1b%7Ccff84bf092fc460bb653e2bc60645528%7C0%7C0%7C638876661566352271%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=RqUx5g%2BMSsbhuz3HhDe9Uk6ca5PwCFilZMFkgrDyky8%3D&amp;reserved=0"><span><em>https://ellenboroughpark.com/</em></span></a><em>. The Japanese Head Spa is priced at £115 per session. For more information, please visit </em><a href="https://eur02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fellenboroughpark.com%2Foffer%2Fjapanese-head-spa%2F&amp;data=