  <p class="">Farlam Hall, a luxurious 18-bedroom <a href="https://eur02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.relaischateaux.com%2Fgb%2F&amp;data=05%7C02%7Cmr%40pc.agency%7Cea9bcb1e37aa4fae443a08ddbef04e1b%7Ccff84bf092fc460bb653e2bc60645528%7C0%7C0%7C638876661566410423%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=1UrZ%2FyFJEh%2FHp8T1VDRtR%2B%2B4h1%2FOd1Imp084vy8xxgg%3D&amp;reserved=0"><span>Relais &amp; Châteaux</span> </a>and <a href="https://eur02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fpobhotels.com%2F%3Fgad_source%3D1%26gclid%3DCj0KCQjws-S-BhD2ARIsALssG0ahXChpyoo6mLAuozcVdP4apHjaUuci_0Mgc-23CYHpqPX4BGNde94aAtcnEALw_wcB&amp;data=05%7C02%7Cmr%40pc.agency%7Cea9bcb1e37aa4fae443a08ddbef04e1b%7Ccff84bf092fc460bb653e2bc60645528%7C0%7C0%7C638876661566423961%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=in1IaaTfXSLenu%2FY%2FLFzBRS1vZ1wYi%2F3NX4n2t6WdSM%3D&amp;reserved=0"><span>PoB Hotel</span></a> known for its world-class hospitality and Michelin-starred dining, is the ideal destination to switch off from the hustle and bustle of everyday life. Surrounded by stunning British countryside, the hotel provides the chance for guests to reconnect with nature, with the North Pennines Mountain range and Hadrian’s Wall just a short drive away. Additionally, Farlam Hall offers a truly unique stargazing experience which, as studies have shown, promotes mental well-being by reducing stress and improving sleep, making it a true retreat for the soul.&nbsp;</p><p class="">The hotel’s must-try “<a href="https://eur02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffarlamhall.com%2Foffers-packages%2Flet-s-go-walking%2F&amp;data=05%7C02%7Cmr%40pc.agency%7Cea9bcb1e37aa4fae443a08ddbef04e1b%7Ccff84bf092fc460bb653e2bc60645528%7C0%7C0%7C638876661566436911%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=Lmbq0HpKoxgArzzsi%2Fz8bYUZBgEAQdyKW3vok9rAT2E%3D&amp;reserved=0"><span>Let’s go Walking</span></a>” package promotes self-guided walks around the charming Cumbrian countryside, with a delicious packed lunch prepared by the hotel’s talented chefs. All ingredients are thoughtfully sourced from the hotel’s own on-site kitchen garden, ensuring every meal is as nourishing as possible - leaving guests feeling good from the inside. Back at the property, guests can continue to enjoy the hotel’s wellness offerings with a GAIA Skincare treatment at <a href="https://eur02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffarlamhall.com%2Fthe-sycamore-retreat%2F&amp;data=05%7C02%7Cmr%40pc.agency%7Cea9bcb1e37aa4fae443a08ddbef04e1b%7Ccff84bf092fc460bb653e2bc60645528%7C0%7C0%7C638876661566449908%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=qZT%2F%2FPbsUGj5P0LVO8q4ZGGUWFO7bEzKLWLt%2FCoEnfc%3D&amp;reserved=0"><span>The Sycamore Retreat</span></a>, launched in April 2025, a healing environment which embraces natural and holistic principles.&nbsp;</p><p class=""><br><strong><em>HOW:</em></strong> <em>Farlam Hall’s Lets go Walking package is priced from £938 per couple. Midweek room rates start at £340 per night and weekend room rates £390 on a B&amp;B basis. For more information please visit </em><a href="https://eur02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffarlamhall.com%2F&amp;data=05%7C02%7Cmr%40pc.agency%7Cea9bcb1e37aa4fae443a08ddbef04e1b%7Ccff84bf092fc460bb653e2bc60645528%7C0%7C0%7C638876661566462818%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=BEzsH2h4cvwlrEUo8UtGmXxdT34Ua2BBCjVh7vAG9x4%3D&amp;reserved=0"><span><em>https://farlamhall.com/</em></span></a><em> / </em><a href="https://eur02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fsearch%3Fq%3Dfarlam%2Bhall%26sca_esv%3D01db24c8ddd18a27%26rlz%3D1C5CHFA_enGB1129GB1135%26ei%3DyExpZ6u_F8iLhbIP9NC3wQ8%26ved%3D0ahUKEwirw_L-572KAxXIRUEAHXToLfgQ4dUDCBA%26uact%3D5%26oq%3Dfarlam%2Bhall%26gs_lp%3DEgxnd3Mtd2l6LXNlcnAiC2ZhcmxhbSBoYWxsMgoQABiwAxjWBBhHMgoQABiwAxjWBBhHMgoQABiwAxjWBBhHMgoQABiwAxjWBBhHMgoQABiwAxjWBBhHMgoQABiwAxjWBBhHMgoQABiwAxjWBBhHMgoQABiwAxjWBBhHSLkFUKEDWIcEcAF4AJABAJgBiwKgAYsCqgEDMi0xuAEDyAEA-AEBmAIBoAIGmAMAiAYBkAYIkgcBMaAH4QQ%26sclient%3Dgws-wiz-serp&amp;data=05%7C02%7Cmr%40pc.agency%7Cea9bcb1e37aa4fae443a08ddbef04e1b%7Ccff84bf092fc460bb653e2bc60645528%7C0%7C0%7C638876661566475896%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=rVNgXlYq2pFVp4gKzOtIXT2oN8w9ciJQnpNvoVsLr%2BU%3D&amp;reserved=0"><span><em>016977 46234</em></span></a></p><p class="">&nbsp;<strong>Escape to Secluded Scottish Hotel, Glenapp Castle, for a Digital Detox</strong></p>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
