  <p class=""><a href="https://eur02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.glenappcastle.com%2F&amp;data=05%7C02%7Cmr%40pc.agency%7Cea9bcb1e37aa4fae443a08ddbef04e1b%7Ccff84bf092fc460bb653e2bc60645528%7C0%7C0%7C638876661566521509%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=18YD1tUXAOxgw8qVoTnxBmbNhSeWZChsvHmz0t%2BRlFM%3D&amp;reserved=0"><span>Glenapp Castle</span></a> is a 21-bedroom majestic Relais &amp; Châteaux Hotel tucked away on the breath-taking Ayrshire coast and is home to The Castle Penthouse Suite, the largest in Scotland. This stunning location offers the ideal getaway; a couple of nights of luxury, in a secluded Castle away from the everyday pressures of life, which can do wonders for one’s psyche. Guests can lose themselves within the Castle’s 110 acres of private estate, manicured gardens, and local woodland, or escape to the exquisite Scottish countryside for long romantic walks and beautiful views of Ailsa Craig and Northern Ireland.&nbsp;</p><p class="">Visitors at the hotel can choose from the 70+ indoor and outdoor <a href="https://eur02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fglenappcastle.com%2Factivities-experiences%2F&amp;data=05%7C02%7Cmr%40pc.agency%7Cea9bcb1e37aa4fae443a08ddbef04e1b%7Ccff84bf092fc460bb653e2bc60645528%7C0%7C0%7C638876661566534887%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=vtML3TPdWCgNFeUh9NASAPgveCYFWihZkdZNdmaDlW4%3D&amp;reserved=0"><span>activities</span></a> to try, with wellness-focused experiences such as in-room treatments, digital detoxes and yoga all available. The team encourages visitors to explore the stunning Scottish landscape by partaking in activities such as cold-water swimming and wild swimming, which improve circulation and reduce stress levels. Whether taking a dip in a local Loch or taking the plunge into the wonderful Scottish seas, swimming in these natural bodies of water is the ultimate way to refresh, invigorate and get back in touch with nature. Alternatively, for those keen to remain outside and connected to nature then forest bathing is a must, where guests will venture deep into the woodland areas of the Glenapp Estate, experiencing guided meditation and mindfulness techniques which help to focus the senses.&nbsp;</p><p class=""><strong><em>HOW:</em></strong><em> Room rates for Glenapp Castle’s Garden View Suites start from £625 on a B&amp;B basis. Forest Bathing is priced at £360 for 1-4 guests per half-day and Wild Swimming is priced at £320 for 1-4 guests. For more information please visit </em><a href="https://eur02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.glenappcastle.com%2F&amp;data=05%7C02%7Cmr%40pc.agency%7Cea9bcb1e37aa4fae443a08ddbef04e1b%7Ccff84bf092fc460bb653e2bc60645528%7C0%7C0%7C638876661566548080%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=Uwdm61bdQi7m%2By%2B6WYICZMTsNl3ENWLuvFA7jLjowEM%3D&amp;reserved=0"><span><em>www.glenappcastle.com</em></span></a><em> / 01465 831212.</em></p><p class="">&nbsp;<strong>Where Time Slows: The Effortless Elegance of Treville Positano</strong></p>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
