                <img data-stretch="false" data-image="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/c3da15da-8a90-4d36-a2e5-1181121ef88f/ANAALA_23.jpg" data-image-dimensions="5262x3508" data-image-focal-point="0.5,0.5" alt="" data-load="false" elementtiming="system-image-block" src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/c3da15da-8a90-4d36-a2e5-1181121ef88f/ANAALA_23.jpg?format=1000w" width="5262" height="3508" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, (max-width: 767px) 100vw, 100vw" onload="this.classList.add(&quot;loaded&quot;)" srcset="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/c3da15da-8a90-4d36-a2e5-1181121ef88f/ANAALA_23.jpg?format=100w 100w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/c3da15da-8a90-4d36-a2e5-1181121ef88f/ANAALA_23.jpg?format=300w 300w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/c3da15da-8a90-4d36-a2e5-1181121ef88f/ANAALA_23.jpg?format=500w 500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/c3da15da-8a90-4d36-a2e5-1181121ef88f/ANAALA_23.jpg?format=750w 750w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/c3da15da-8a90-4d36-a2e5-1181121ef88f/ANAALA_23.jpg?format=1000w 1000w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/c3da15da-8a90-4d36-a2e5-1181121ef88f/ANAALA_23.jpg?format=1500w 1500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/c3da15da-8a90-4d36-a2e5-1181121ef88f/ANAALA_23.jpg?format=2500w 2500w" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-loader="sqs">

            
          
        
          
        

        
      
        </figure>
      

    
  


  





  <p class="">There’s no fear of missing out when everything travellers need is already here. Set along the tranquil shores of Phang Nga beach in Thailand, <a href="https://eur02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inialathailand.com%2F&amp;data=05%7C02%7Cmr%40pc.agency%7Cea9bcb1e37aa4fae443a08ddbef04e1b%7Ccff84bf092fc460bb653e2bc60645528%7C0%7C0%7C638876661566795557%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=oijQrkYImRMnDRR%2BWSmbLoc%2BicLIidFO6IGA0kDCN%2BY%3D&amp;reserved=0"><span>Iniala Beach House</span></a> invites guests to forget the outside world and embrace the joy of missing out. Every element is designed to nourish mind, body, and spirit, creating a rare opportunity to disconnect completely, and reconnect with what truly matters.</p><p class="">Wellness lies at the heart of every guest experience.<a href="https://eur02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inialathailand.com%2Ffacilities%2F%3Fsection%3Dspa&amp;data=05%7C02%7Cmr%40pc.agency%7Cea9bcb1e37aa4fae443a08ddbef04e1b%7Ccff84bf092fc460bb653e2bc60645528%7C0%7C0%7C638876661566808970%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=t3NSJDtwb7ijSU05fouz5r4qAjBt%2BiHsr%2FDkfn8F8%2BY%3D&amp;reserved=0"> <span>The Pearl Spa</span></a>, with its mother-of-pearl interiors and Zen garden skylight, offers serene treatments for all guests. Those staying in the Lotus or Siamese Suites can also access The Golden Temple Bell Spa, an ethereal sanctuary inspired by mountain temples of northern Thailand, with herbal steam rituals and sacred design details. Beyond the spa, wellbeing <a href="https://eur02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inialathailand.com%2Ffacilities%2F%3Fsection%3Dspa&amp;data=05%7C02%7Cmr%40pc.agency%7Cea9bcb1e37aa4fae443a08ddbef04e1b%7Ccff84bf092fc460bb653e2bc60645528%7C0%7C0%7C638876661566824080%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=drSdL2htE9W9ZXAEl9LbeKLxRE3c%2FazUb172tE%2BS7Bs%3D&amp;reserved=0"><span>activities</span></a>&nbsp; continues with beach boot camps at sunrise, sunset yoga, Thai boxing, and paddleboarding, all encouraging guests to be fully present in their surroundings and forget the outside world's temptations. At Iniala Beach House, switching off feels natural. It’s not about what guests are missing; it’s about what they’re finally free to enjoy: stillness, connection, and a sense of total presence.</p><p class=""><strong>HOW:</strong> <em>Room rates at Iniala Beach House Thailand start from $1,050 (£825) per night (Pool Residences) and Villas start from $3,500 (£2,750) per night. For more information, please visit </em><a href="https://eur02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inialathailand.com%2F&amp;data=05%7C02%7Cmr%40pc.agency%7Cea9bcb1e37aa4fae443a08ddbef04e1b%7Ccff84bf092fc460bb653e2bc60645528%7C0%7C0%7C638876661566837488%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=IL25WWz36bl5D2nfTz%2FXdnbRheL1brJxuRCHmUxzCJk%3D&amp;reserved=0"><span><em>https://www.inialathailand.com/</em></span></a><em> </em><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p><p class=""><strong>The Art of Switching off at The Xara Palace</strong></p>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
        <figure class="
              sqs-block-image-figure
              intrinsic
