        </figure>
      

    
  


  





  <p class="">For those craving a slower pace and a chance to truly switch off this summer, <a href="https://eur02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fxarapalace.com.mt%2F&amp;data=05%7C02%7Cmr%40pc.agency%7Cea9bcb1e37aa4fae443a08ddbef04e1b%7Ccff84bf092fc460bb653e2bc60645528%7C0%7C0%7C638876661566877253%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=eMJ6GUbCIDal%2FhrES0x8jCu8LIj3BfO2gBMr%2FUeKttE%3D&amp;reserved=0"><span>The Xara Palace</span></a> offers a refreshing escape from the constant hum of connectivity. Found within the fortified walls of Mdina,&nbsp; one of Europe’s best-preserved medieval cities, this 17th-century palazzo invites guests to embrace a different kind of luxury: the joy of missing out. Here, guests would rather linger in stillness than scroll, preferring time spent wandering quiet cobbled streets, basking in golden hour light atop ancient bastions, and rediscovering the simple pleasures of travel.</p><p class="">With just 17 individually designed rooms and suites, each thoughtfully furnished with antiques, rich textiles, and sweeping island views, The Xara Palace blends charm with serene exclusivity. Culinary excellence completes the experience. For those seeking an extra touch of exclusivity, the newly unveiled <a href="https://eur02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fxarapalace.com.mt%2Fpalazzino-belvedere%2F&amp;data=05%7C02%7Cmr%40pc.agency%7Cea9bcb1e37aa4fae443a08ddbef04e1b%7Ccff84bf092fc460bb653e2bc60645528%7C0%7C0%7C638876661566890316%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=5fcJJGYW42%2BctN5%2FTtHZzUHyAmn0EhZv%2BVroNM%2BDw%2BA%3D&amp;reserved=0"><span>Palazzino Belvedere</span></a> offers guests their very own hideaway, a stone's throw away from the main hotel. This most romantic and glorious retreat invites guests to truly immerse themselves in Malta's rich past. Enjoy refined seasonal dishes at the Michelin-starred <a href="https://eur02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fdemondion.xaracollection.com%2F&amp;data=05%7C02%7Cmr%40pc.agency%7Cea9bcb1e37aa4fae443a08ddbef04e1b%7Ccff84bf092fc460bb653e2bc60645528%7C0%7C0%7C638876661566903540%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=rV%2FpW%2BFQn7mCacMsNWVWIWUAJsE%2F6u70lqPUx6onu%2F4%3D&amp;reserved=0"><span>de Mondion</span></a>, or Mediterranean classics at <a href="https://eur02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fxarapalace.com.mt%2Fdining%2Ftrattoria-ad-1530%2F&amp;data=05%7C02%7Cmr%40pc.agency%7Cea9bcb1e37aa4fae443a08ddbef04e1b%7Ccff84bf092fc460bb653e2bc60645528%7C0%7C0%7C638876661566916704%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=Ka35sGWIM8JE337nz8HtIMRL4oDBli%2BSKAVxea9F8tw%3D&amp;reserved=0"><span>Trattoria AD 1530</span></a>, set al fresco in the picturesque piazza. Offering tranquillity, cultural richness, and impeccable service, The Xara Palace is a mindful alternative to Europe’s busier summer destinations, ideal for those craving a quiet moment away from it all.</p><p class=""><strong>HOW:</strong> <em>Rooms at The Xara Palace start from €236 (£196) per night per room. For more information, please visit </em><a href="https://eur02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.xarapalace.com.mt%2F&amp;data=05%7C02%7Cmr%40pc.agency%7Cea9bcb1e37aa4fae443a08ddbef04e1b%7Ccff84bf092fc460bb653e2bc60645528%7C0%7C0%7C638876661566929705%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=L%2Fol%2BWUB1F3dX6zd0MOcbzCS2xWp7b3cnOVHFQ2cf5I%3D&amp;reserved=0"><span><em>www.xarapalace.com.mt</em></span></a></p><p class=""><strong><em>For all media enquiries, please contact </em></strong><a href="mailto:hotelpod@pc.agency?" target="_blank"><strong><em>hotelpod@pc.agency</em></strong></a><strong><em>.</em></strong></p>]]></content:encoded><media:content type="image/jpeg" url="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/1752654686542-GM7KLBNSXV2R5MC6RG9K/1D6A0145.jpg?format=1500w" medium="image" isDefault="true" width="1500" height="968"><media:title type="plain">The Joy of Missing Out; ‘JOMO’ Travel Destinations That Celebrate Disconnection</media:title></media:content></item><item><title>ATM 2025: Key Insights from the Middle East’s Premier Travel Event</title><dc:creator>Mia Ryan</dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 23 May 2025 10:51:40 +0000</pubDate><link>https://www.pc.agency/blog/atm-2025-key-insights</link><guid isPermaLink="false">6595a9416580d436d022fb21:6686698fa6726e39557b3ada:683050ad229c885906a8b7df</guid><description><![CDATA[Immersive experiences, microtrend-driven itineraries, and deeper guest 
connections are reshaping luxury travel in the Middle East. Fresh from ATM 
2025, here’s what the industry’s top voices are saying - and how to stay 
ahead.]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p class="">In early May, The PC Agency attended the <a href="https://www.wtm.com/atm/en-gb.html"><span>Arabian Travel Market</span></a> (ATM) at the <a href="https://www.dwtc.com/en/"><span>Dubai World Trade Centre</span></a>, a key gathering for professionals across the global travel sector. As a longstanding presence in the region, we used this opportunity to immerse ourselves in the latest trends, network with influential media, and discuss strategies to meet the evolving demands of the luxury travel market.</p><p class=""><strong>The Rise of Immersive, Experience-Driven Travel</strong></p>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
        <figure class="
              sqs-block-image-figure
