                <img data-stretch="false" data-image="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/b03d19e3-9118-4bb1-ba3e-a4105d5a6b31/Farlam.jpg" data-image-dimensions="1200x799" data-image-focal-point="0.5,0.5" alt="" data-load="false" elementtiming="system-image-block" src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/b03d19e3-9118-4bb1-ba3e-a4105d5a6b31/Farlam.jpg?format=1000w" width="1200" height="799" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, (max-width: 767px) 100vw, 100vw" onload="this.classList.add(&quot;loaded&quot;)" srcset="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/b03d19e3-9118-4bb1-ba3e-a4105d5a6b31/Farlam.jpg?format=100w 100w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/b03d19e3-9118-4bb1-ba3e-a4105d5a6b31/Farlam.jpg?format=300w 300w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/b03d19e3-9118-4bb1-ba3e-a4105d5a6b31/Farlam.jpg?format=500w 500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/b03d19e3-9118-4bb1-ba3e-a4105d5a6b31/Farlam.jpg?format=750w 750w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/b03d19e3-9118-4bb1-ba3e-a4105d5a6b31/Farlam.jpg?format=1000w 1000w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/b03d19e3-9118-4bb1-ba3e-a4105d5a6b31/Farlam.jpg?format=1500w 1500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/b03d19e3-9118-4bb1-ba3e-a4105d5a6b31/Farlam.jpg?format=2500w 2500w" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-loader="sqs">

            
          
        
          
        

        
      
        </figure>
      

    
  


  





  <p class="">At <a href="http://farlamhall.com" target="_blank">Farlam Hall Hotel</a>, celestial observations conclude with culinary celebrations as the award-winning kitchen team transforms locally sourced ingredients from its garden into memorable feasts. Situated in a secluded area of Northumberland, the hotel stands as a gateway to some of Britain's most pristine night skies. These serene landscapes, paired with the famously clear and starry skies, create a truly divine stargazing experience. Northumberland National Park is home to some of the clearest night skies in the UK, making it one of the best stargazing locations in the country. In these pristine skies, the Andromeda Galaxy, located 2.5 million light-years away, can be seen with the naked eye - showcasing the area's exceptional conditions.</p><p class=""><strong>For more information, visit</strong><a href="https://www.visitfinland.com/en/"><strong> </strong></a><a href="http://farlamhall.com"><span><strong><em>farlamhall.com.</em></strong></span></a></p>]]></content:encoded><media:content type="image/jpeg" url="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/1741780753554-H7KF3BCUPMCA9H0G9XM4/joshua-earle-C6duwascOEA-unsplash+%281%29.jpg?format=1500w" medium="image" isDefault="true" width="1500" height="1000"><media:title type="plain">Noctourism: A Guide to the Best Stargazing Experiences Around the World</media:title></media:content></item><item><title>International Women’s Day: Empowering Female Stories from Around the World</title><dc:creator>Mia Ryan</dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 11:23:13 +0000</pubDate><link>https://www.pc.agency/blog/international-womens-day</link><guid isPermaLink="false">6595a9416580d436d022fb21:6686698fa6726e39557b3ada:67cace1f5df6f57be378b7ea</guid><description><![CDATA[This International Women’s Day, we’re exploring some of the most inspiring 
female-led stories from our clients, and unveiling the empowering 
destinations where women are redefining travel, culture, and wellness.]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p class="">This International Women’s Day, we’re taking a moment to celebrate the incredible women who are shaping the world in various industries, from hospitality and art to wildlife and adventure. Across continents and cultures, women are redefining what it means to lead, inspire, and make a lasting impact. </p><p class="">Join us as we explore some of the most inspiring female-led stories from our clients, and discover the empowering destinations where women are redefining travel, culture, and wellness.</p><p class="sqsrte-large"><strong>Explore Dubai’s Culture and Heritage with Female-Owned Frying Pan Adventures</strong></p><p class="">Operated and founded by two sisters, Arva and Farida Ahmed, <a href="https://eur02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=http%3A%2F%2Ffryingpanadventures.com%2F&amp;data=05%7C02%7Cemk%40pc.agency%7Cfd707a60230f4b11265c08dd4764dfaf%7Ccff84bf092fc460bb653e2bc60645528%7C0%7C0%7C638745220820656256%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=W41FBLQhhYzEcFRq7QMYyWEB%2BwrJHMsfblRIwRc1yo4%3D&amp;reserved=0" target="_blank">Frying Pan Adventures</a> aims to showcase Bur Dubai and Deira's hidden restaurants and street food stalls. Arva and Farida grew up in Dubai during the 1980s and were raised learning about the untold stories of chefs and stall vendors that gave the city its cultural identity, many of which are still thriving today. Created to educate visitors on Emirati food and culture, Arva and Farida founded Frying Pan Adventures based on their passion for preserving Dubai's food stories and sense of community.&nbsp;</p>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
