  <p class="sqsrte-large"><strong>Transformative Female Solo Adventures with Kamba Africa</strong></p><p class=""><a href="https://kambaafrica.com/"><span>Kamba African Rainforest Experiences</span></a> offers luxury lodges and adventurous rainforest expeditions for female solo travellers seeking transformational travel experiences in the peaceful and welcoming Republic of the Congo (ROC), home to the world’s second-largest rainforest after the Amazon. Founded by Sabine Plattner and now led by her daughter, Managing Director Kristina Plattner, Kamba’s female-led team offer incredible itineraries, expert female guides and warm hospitality, ensuring female travellers experience an accommodating and engaging adventure in the ROC.</p>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
