          <figcaption class="image-caption-wrapper">
            <p data-rte-preserve-empty="true"><em>Farlam Hall’s Lets go Walking package is priced from £938 per couple. Midweek room rates start at £340 per night and weekend room rates £390 on a B&amp;B basis. For more information please visit </em><a href="https://eur02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffarlamhall.com%2F&amp;data=05%7C02%7Cmr%40pc.agency%7C35d492e941994cbc8d6508dd57545dac%7Ccff84bf092fc460bb653e2bc60645528%7C0%7C0%7C638762742078168205%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=nG7ZEsb9ldNH5WhQWgE2njRY3mKFjsO0%2FYjuLXn2ncY%3D&amp;reserved=0"><em>https://farlamhall.com/</em></a></p>
          </figcaption>
        
      
        </figure>
      

    
  


  





  <p class="sqsrte-large"><strong>Enjoy the Ultimate Girl’s Takeover at Glenapp Castle</strong></p><p class="">Home to the penthouse largest suite in Scotland, <a href="https://glenappcastle.com/"><span>Glenapp Castle</span></a> is the perfect hotel for those looking to escape to the Scottish coast to enjoy a secluded girls’ trip. With over 70+ activities for any bonding activities, guests can grab their closest girlfriends and take over thewhole top floor of this fairy tale castle. From falconry to archery, to perfume making and the <a href="https://eur02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kitchencoosandewes.com%2F&amp;data=05%7C02%7Cmr%40pc.agency%7C35d492e941994cbc8d6508dd57545dac%7Ccff84bf092fc460bb653e2bc60645528%7C0%7C0%7C638762742078227721%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=oEKDpuYguk4a%2BUOJ1IR8z4jWMvGGAfxF9Q7a2%2BE7aa0%3D&amp;reserved=0"><span>Kitchen Coos and Ewes</span></a> experience where visitors can meet a herd of very special Highland cows all before finishing off the evening with a seven course tasting dinner in the Castle Dining Room, or in the more private seclusion of the dining room in the suite itself.</p>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
