  <p class="sqsrte-large"><strong>Serene Solo Surfing in La Sultana Oualidia, Morocco</strong></p><p class="">Explore the tranquil setting of <a href="https://www.lasultanahotels.com/oualidia"><span>La Sultana Oualidia</span></a>, a beguiling Moorish fortress that overlooks a stunning saltwater lagoon on the Atlantic Coast. Located in the quaint fishing village of Oualidia, known as Morocco’s ‘oyster capital’ when the tide recedes, this luxury boutique hotel is made of 12 individually designed rooms and suites, each with its own private terrace and sea water Jacuzzi. Ideal for female solo travellers, or made for the perfect girls getaway, the hotel offers a curated variety of immersive experiences and excursions.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
