  <p class="sqsrte-large"><strong>Veni, Vidi, Vici: A Luxurious Girls Trip to Rhinoceros Roma</strong></p><p class=""><a href="https://eur02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Frhinocerosroma.com%2Fen%2Fhome-slider-ing%2F&amp;data=05%7C02%7Cmr%40pc.agency%7C35d492e941994cbc8d6508dd57545dac%7Ccff84bf092fc460bb653e2bc60645528%7C0%7C0%7C638762742078329297%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=%2BpuM5UJNs1ULZDbwikeJYTsrFfOhK7COZja0zZMKfgQ%3D&amp;reserved=0"><span>Rhinoceros Roma</span></a> is the ultimate location for an unforgettable long weekend in the Eternal City. ust 2.5 hours from London, this boutique establishment offers the perfect girls trip destination combining a unique blend of luxury, art and central location. From the expansive two level rooftop terrace offering cocktails and panoramic views across the red roofs of Rome to the stylish design-centric apartments, the establishment is perfectly placed for a cultural excursion to Rome in its Jubilee year.&nbsp;</p>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
