            "
        >
          
        
        

        
          
            
          
            
                
                
                
                
                
                
                
                <img data-stretch="false" data-image="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/41854062-bc3e-4756-8fd1-3efad7f91d92/Floating+Dispenser+%282%29.jpg" data-image-dimensions="1920x1080" data-image-focal-point="0.5,0.5" alt="" data-load="false" elementtiming="system-image-block" src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/41854062-bc3e-4756-8fd1-3efad7f91d92/Floating+Dispenser+%282%29.jpg?format=1000w" width="1920" height="1080" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, (max-width: 767px) 100vw, 100vw" onload="this.classList.add(&quot;loaded&quot;)" srcset="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/41854062-bc3e-4756-8fd1-3efad7f91d92/Floating+Dispenser+%282%29.jpg?format=100w 100w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/41854062-bc3e-4756-8fd1-3efad7f91d92/Floating+Dispenser+%282%29.jpg?format=300w 300w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/41854062-bc3e-4756-8fd1-3efad7f91d92/Floating+Dispenser+%282%29.jpg?format=500w 500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/41854062-bc3e-4756-8fd1-3efad7f91d92/Floating+Dispenser+%282%29.jpg?format=750w 750w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/41854062-bc3e-4756-8fd1-3efad7f91d92/Floating+Dispenser+%282%29.jpg?format=1000w 1000w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/41854062-bc3e-4756-8fd1-3efad7f91d92/Floating+Dispenser+%282%29.jpg?format=1500w 1500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/41854062-bc3e-4756-8fd1-3efad7f91d92/Floating+Dispenser+%282%29.jpg?format=2500w 2500w" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-loader="sqs">

            
          
        
          
        

        
      
        </figure>
      

    
  


  





  <p class="">With over 40 years of creative collaboration, Molton Brown has crafted unrivalled sensorial experiences across the world's most distinctive hotels to enhance guests' indulgent moments. Rooted in London’s diverse creative spirit, Molton Brown brings a vivid, enlivening approach that enriches the ordinary to create the extraordinary – transforming each hotel stay into a journey where nature, memory and culture connect.</p><p class="">In November 2024, Molton Brown introduced the Floating Dispenser, further enhancing the brand’s sleek modern packaging solutions, providing partners with an elevated amenities experience. Available in select fragrances, these easy to install wall-mounted dispensers are designed with an invisible wall bracket and discreet fill indicator, offering a modern, minimalist aesthetic that reduces plastic waste and are designed to be sleek and durable.&nbsp;</p><p class="">Alongside this launch, the brand continues to celebrate its Reviving Rosemary collection which is made to uplift the senses, and has become a cornerstone of its hotel amenities offering. This thoughtfully crafted aromatherapy collection joins an extensive range of signature fragrances, including Coastal Cypress &amp; Sea Fennel, Orange &amp; Bergamot, Heavenly Gingerlily, Fiery Pink Pepper and Mandarin &amp; Clary Sage.&nbsp;</p><p class="">Beyond the core collections of bath, body, hair and hand products designed to be layered together, Molton Brown offers hotel partners a comprehensive suite of luxury hotel amenities, home collections and tailored services. Through a truly unique omnichannel experience, the brand provides tailored services including VIP gifting programmes, in-store events, a fragrance butler, digital marketing initiatives and staff training, enabling hotel partners to enhance guest experiences that extends beyond the traditional hospitality touchpoints.</p><p class="">As pioneers of positive luxury, Molton Brown has continued to innovate since 1971 with an uncompromising approach to quality ingredients and sustainability. Proudly manufacturing products in England and committed to never testing on animals, the brand works in harmony with nature and people. The brand also uses 50% recycled PET in its packaging and offers five litre refill solutions within its dispensing programme to reduce single-use bottles, showcasing what’s possible when sustainability meets creativity.</p>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
