  <p class=""><strong><em>HOW:</em></strong><em> For more information, please visit </em><a href="http://www.moltonbrown.co.uk/store/hotel-amenities"><span><em>www.moltonbrown.co.uk/store/hotel-amenities</em></span></a></p><p class=""><strong><em>For media enquiries, please contact Paul Charles / Anastasia Mackaness-Mills / Rosie Atkins / Tahli Brittain / Freddie Wilson via </em></strong><a href="mailto:moltonbrown@pc.agency"><span><em>moltonbrown@pc.agency</em></span></a></p><p class=""><br><br><br><br></p>]]></content:encoded><media:content type="image/jpeg" url="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/1741173462643-7RZ3M5AY5P0A75KRPI9H/Reviving+Rosemary+-+Hotel+Collection+%281%29+%281%29_1.jpg?format=1500w" medium="image" isDefault="true" width="1500" height="1000"><media:title type="plain">Molton Brown appoints The PC Agency as its Dedicated Hotel Amenities PR Partner</media:title></media:content></item><item><title>The Rise of Bleisure Travel: How Asia is Redefining Work-Life Balance</title><dc:creator>Mia Ryan</dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 08:56:15 +0000</pubDate><link>https://www.pc.agency/blog/bleisure-travel-asia</link><guid isPermaLink="false">6595a9416580d436d022fb21:6686698fa6726e39557b3ada:679b83e652d66454ab67c50d</guid><description><![CDATA[Asia is transforming business trips into exciting getaways for working 
professionals in Australia and the wider Asia Pacific region, as the rise 
of bleisure travel blends work and leisure seamlessly for unforgettable 
trips.]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p class="">Imagine stepping off a plane in Singapore after a business meeting, only to find yourself sipping cocktails at Marina Bay Sands while the city lights twinkle below. Or picture a post-conference day spent in Tokyo, wandering through neon-lit Shibuya before soaking in a tranquil onsen in the countryside. For many Australian professionals, this seamless blend of work and leisure - known as <a href="https://www.corporatetraveller.com.au/resources/insights/bleisure-travel"><span>bleisure travel</span></a> - is no longer a luxury but an essential part of their travel experience.</p><p class=""><strong>The Bleisure Boom</strong></p>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
