  <p class="">Few destinations exude cinematic romance like Italy’s Amalfi Coast, where sheer cliffs meet turquoise waters and ancient towns cling to the rugged coastline. At <a href="https://villatreville.com/"><span>Treville Positano</span></a>, travelers can step into the world of legendary filmmaker Franco Zeffirelli, renowned for iconic films such as <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Romeo_and_Juliet_(1968_film)"><span>Romeo and Juliet</span></a>, <a href="https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0061407/"><span>The Taming of the Shrew</span></a>, and <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tea_with_Mussolini"><span>Tea with Mussolini</span></a>. Zeffirelli’s former villa has been transformed into an ultra-luxurious retreat, preserving the creative spirit and allure of its famous owner.</p><p class="">Perched on a cliff with breathtaking views of Positano and the Tyrrhenian Sea, <a href="https://villatreville.com/"><span>Treville Positano</span></a> seamlessly combines cosmopolitan glamour with serene natural beauty. The estate features opulent suites filled with curated art and antiques, sprawling gardens with citrus groves, and a private beach. Guests can indulge in exceptional cuisine inspired by local ingredients at <a href="https://villatreville.com/maestros-restaurant/"><span>Maestro’s</span></a>, the villa’s signature restaurant, or rejuvenate at the in-house spa. This property captures the Amalfi Coast’s timeless charm while inviting visitors to live out their own cinematic fantasies.</p>]]></content:encoded><media:content type="image/jpeg" url="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/1738245065370-F5QFETROMZ6393L8QF92/pexels-tomfisk-30427611.jpg?format=1500w" medium="image" isDefault="true" width="1500" height="1000"><media:title type="plain">Set-Jetting: Luxury Escapes to Iconic Movie Locations</media:title></media:content></item><item><title>Beyond the Skyline: Unforgettable Weekend Getaways from Dubai</title><dc:creator>Mia Ryan</dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 14:23:01 +0000</pubDate><link>https://www.pc.agency/blog/weekend-getaways-from-dubai</link><guid isPermaLink="false">6595a9416580d436d022fb21:6686698fa6726e39557b3ada:679a394f4a5b3f39c8f58ec3</guid><description><![CDATA[Dubai's best-kept secret? These jaw-dropping weekend escapes are closer 
than you think.]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p class=""><a href="https://www.visitdubai.com/en/"><span>Dubai</span></a> is more than just a city of iconic skyscrapers, luxury shopping, and world-class dining; it’s a hub of endless possibilities for both exploration and relaxation. Beyond its global allure, Dubai itself is a treasure trove of experiences for a weekend escape without even needing to board a plane. From its pristine beaches and thrilling desert adventures to its vibrant cultural scene and unmatched hospitality, Dubai caters to every kind of traveller. Whether you’re sipping coffee at a chic café in <a href="https://www.visitdubai.com/en/explore-dubai/dubai-neighbourhoods/palm-jumeirah"><span>Jumeirah</span></a>, enjoying the sunset at <a href="https://www.visitdubai.com/en/places-to-visit/kite-beach"><span>Kite Beach</span></a>, or marveling at the <a href="https://www.visitdubai.com/en/places-to-visit/the-dubai-fountain"><span>Dubai Fountain</span></a>’s spectacular display, the city has an incredible way of making you feel like you’ve travelled far and wide without leaving its borders.</p><p class="">If you’re looking to venture abroad, Dubai’s strategic location makes it a gateway to some of the world’s most captivating destinations. With exceptional flight connectivity and short-haul options from carriers such as <a href="https://www.etihad.com/en-gb/"><span>Etihad</span></a>, <a href="https://www.turkishairlines.com/"><span>Turkish Airlines</span></a> or <a href="https://www.emirates.com/uk/english/" target="_blank">Emirates</a>, you can step into a completely different world within just a few hours. Whether you crave a serene beach retreat, a rich cultural adventure, or a vibrant city break, these nearby destinations promise unforgettable experiences.&nbsp;</p><p class=""><strong>The Seychelles</strong></p>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
