  <p class="">For those dreaming of pristine beaches and lush landscapes, the Seychelles is a must-visit. Just a direct flight from Dubai to Mahé, this Indian Ocean gem offers the ultimate escape for weekend getaways from Dubai. Upon arrival, immerse yourself in the vibrant culture by exploring the colorful street food markets, where fresh fish and tropical fruits tempt every palate.</p><p class="">Adventurous travellers can venture beyond Mahé to uncover the archipelago’s lesser-known treasures. A boat trip to the <a href="https://www.aldabraislands.com/"><span>Aldabra Islands</span></a>, a UNESCO World Heritage site, reveals an underwater paradise perfect for diving and snorkeling. Imagine swimming alongside manta rays and sea turtles while surrounded by coral reefs teeming with life. The Seychelles isn’t just a destination; it’s a dreamscape for anyone seeking natural beauty and tranquillity.</p><p class=""><strong>The Maldives</strong></p>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
