  <p class="">A mere four-hour flight separates Dubai from Male, the gateway to the <a href="https://visitmaldives.com/en"><span>Maldives</span></a>. Renowned for its overwater villas and turquoise lagoons, this island nation is synonymous with luxury and seclusion, making it one of the top short breaks Dubai travellers favour.</p><p class="">Unwind in your private villa, where the lapping waves serve as your soundtrack, or explore the rich marine life through scuba diving and snorkeling excursions. The Maldives is particularly appealing for those looking to disconnect from the world and recharge in serene surroundings. Whether indulging in bespoke spa treatments or dining on fresh seafood under the stars, every moment here is designed to soothe the soul.</p><p class=""><strong>Morocco</strong></p>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
