                <img data-stretch="false" data-image="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/807e8b36-33d0-4c31-9354-7354aec334ab/luca-bravo-O453M2Liufs-unsplash.jpg" data-image-dimensions="4896x3264" data-image-focal-point="0.5,0.5" alt="" data-load="false" elementtiming="system-image-block" src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/807e8b36-33d0-4c31-9354-7354aec334ab/luca-bravo-O453M2Liufs-unsplash.jpg?format=1000w" width="4896" height="3264" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, (max-width: 767px) 100vw, 100vw" onload="this.classList.add(&quot;loaded&quot;)" srcset="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/807e8b36-33d0-4c31-9354-7354aec334ab/luca-bravo-O453M2Liufs-unsplash.jpg?format=100w 100w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/807e8b36-33d0-4c31-9354-7354aec334ab/luca-bravo-O453M2Liufs-unsplash.jpg?format=300w 300w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/807e8b36-33d0-4c31-9354-7354aec334ab/luca-bravo-O453M2Liufs-unsplash.jpg?format=500w 500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/807e8b36-33d0-4c31-9354-7354aec334ab/luca-bravo-O453M2Liufs-unsplash.jpg?format=750w 750w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/807e8b36-33d0-4c31-9354-7354aec334ab/luca-bravo-O453M2Liufs-unsplash.jpg?format=1000w 1000w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/807e8b36-33d0-4c31-9354-7354aec334ab/luca-bravo-O453M2Liufs-unsplash.jpg?format=1500w 1500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/807e8b36-33d0-4c31-9354-7354aec334ab/luca-bravo-O453M2Liufs-unsplash.jpg?format=2500w 2500w" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-loader="sqs">

            
          
        
          
        

        
      
        </figure>
      

    
  


  





  <p class="">We are more connected than ever with the world at our fingertips. In this digital age, it is easy to become overwhelmed by options, putting consumers at risk of choice paralysis. Even after honing in on a specific destination, there is still an overwhelming choice when it comes to where to stay and what to do. In this age of excess, consumers are actively searching for a trusted source to manage multi-option shopping and present tailored ideas in one convenient place.&nbsp;</p><p class="">According to <a href="https://www.thedrum.com/news/2023/07/11/path-purchase-travelers-are-it-the-long-haul-advertisers-should-be-too"><span>TripAdvisor</span></a>, more than 80% of holiday planning takes place 2-3 months before booking a trip. During the planning phase, a consumer makes an average of<a href="https://advertising.expedia.com/about/press-releases/retail-and-travel-site-visitation-aligns-consumers-plan-and-book-vacation-packages/"><span> 38 visits to travel related sites</span></a> in the 45 day lead-up to booking a holiday. It is clear that travel is a complex purchase. As digital advancements persist, it is likely the information available to us is only going to increase, therefore furthering the demand for travel professionals to break down the choices and offer the best options for a consumer.</p><p class=""><strong>An Ever-Changing World&nbsp;</strong></p>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
        <figure class="
              sqs-block-image-figure
              intrinsic
