        >
          
        
        

        
          
            
          
            
                
                
                
                
                
                
                
                <img data-stretch="false" data-image="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/ae8b1601-16f5-4731-8293-711c26cf609c/hu-chen-0LwfbRtQ-ac-unsplash+%282%29.jpg" data-image-dimensions="5863x3920" data-image-focal-point="0.5,0.5" alt="" data-load="false" elementtiming="system-image-block" src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/ae8b1601-16f5-4731-8293-711c26cf609c/hu-chen-0LwfbRtQ-ac-unsplash+%282%29.jpg?format=1000w" width="5863" height="3920" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, (max-width: 767px) 100vw, 100vw" onload="this.classList.add(&quot;loaded&quot;)" srcset="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/ae8b1601-16f5-4731-8293-711c26cf609c/hu-chen-0LwfbRtQ-ac-unsplash+%282%29.jpg?format=100w 100w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/ae8b1601-16f5-4731-8293-711c26cf609c/hu-chen-0LwfbRtQ-ac-unsplash+%282%29.jpg?format=300w 300w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/ae8b1601-16f5-4731-8293-711c26cf609c/hu-chen-0LwfbRtQ-ac-unsplash+%282%29.jpg?format=500w 500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/ae8b1601-16f5-4731-8293-711c26cf609c/hu-chen-0LwfbRtQ-ac-unsplash+%282%29.jpg?format=750w 750w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/ae8b1601-16f5-4731-8293-711c26cf609c/hu-chen-0LwfbRtQ-ac-unsplash+%282%29.jpg?format=1000w 1000w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/ae8b1601-16f5-4731-8293-711c26cf609c/hu-chen-0LwfbRtQ-ac-unsplash+%282%29.jpg?format=1500w 1500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/ae8b1601-16f5-4731-8293-711c26cf609c/hu-chen-0LwfbRtQ-ac-unsplash+%282%29.jpg?format=2500w 2500w" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-loader="sqs">

            
          
        
          
        

        
      
        </figure>
      

    
  


  





  <p class="">The global pandemic threw the travel sector into chaos and the disruption that customers experienced has had a lasting impact on the way we choose to plan and book our holidays. It is clear that UK holidaymakers want reassurance and security when making travel plans. As consumers remain unwilling to compromise on their holidays, they are instead increasingly leaning towards trusted travel professionals when planning their trips for the year ahead, according to the <a href="https://travelweeklyinsight.co.uk/"><span>Travel Weekly Insight Report 2024</span></a>. This is a trend particularly prominent among the younger generation as young families and 18-24 year olds are the largest age groups seeking reassurance and booking through trusted agents.</p><p class="">Despite full recovery for the industry being on the horizon, travel disruptions in the future are inevitable. From natural disasters such as the LA wildfires, to industrial action from air traffic control strikes, travellers are increasingly aware of potential disturbances to their holiday plans. In response, travel professionals are able to pave the way for consumers, ensuring quality holiday experiences that are worth the spend, while providing reassurance they can navigate unexpected challenges along the way. <a href="https://www.abta.com/news/abta-reports-rise-people-booking-travel-professionals-latest-holiday-habits-report"><span>ABTA</span></a> reported that ‘reassurance for the consumer’ as a reason for booking through a travel agent increased to 43% in 2024 (up from 34% the previous year).&nbsp;</p><p class=""><strong>Helping You Reach The Trade&nbsp;</strong></p>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
