        </figure>
      

    
  


  





  <p class="">For those chasing truly experiential dining, <a href="https://farlamhall.com/"><span>Farlam Hall</span></a> in Cumbria delivers a masterpiece with the recently launched chef’s table experience, <a href="https://eur02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffarlamhall.com%2Ffood-drink%2Fhrishi-s-table%2F&amp;data=05%7C02%7Cbd%40pc.agency%7C469928e9c178479a367e08dd3ba6c8ce%7Ccff84bf092fc460bb653e2bc60645528%7C0%7C0%7C638732309718813300%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=R0TEcFO9s17gV8fd3SNUfvEaIryPUbl6yryHtz4Jk6E%3D&amp;reserved=0"><span>HRISHI’s Table</span></a>, provides an intimate and innovative private dining setting unlike no other, tailored to appease an array of palettes. Each course is a masterpiece, meticulously crafted to surprise and enchant guests. The unique dining experience will be hosted by Hrishikesh with Senior Sous Chef, Benhur, alongside the knowledgeable front of house team, the culinary ‘storytellers’ who will share the inspiration and processes behind each of the dishes.&nbsp;</p><p class="">The hotel boasts an array of prestigious accolades that reflect the strength of the F&amp;B offerings, such as The <a href="https://eur02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffarlamhall.com%2Ffood-drink%2Fthe-cedar-tree-by-hrishikesh-desai%2F&amp;data=05%7C02%7Cbd%40pc.agency%7C469928e9c178479a367e08dd3ba6c8ce%7Ccff84bf092fc460bb653e2bc60645528%7C0%7C0%7C638732309718799364%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=IBRd8nmnAhJ1de018MVgisCPeSQS4YfxHnTTpeyJng4%3D&amp;reserved=0"><span>Cedar Tree Restaurant</span></a> by Hrishikesh Desai which won its first Michelin Star in February 2024.</p><p class=""><strong>ION Harbour by Simon Rogan</strong></p>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
        <figure class="
              sqs-block-image-figure
              intrinsic
