  <p class=""><strong>The Business Traveller Awards</strong></p><p class=""><a href="https://www.businesstraveller.com/awards/business-traveller-awards-2024/" target="_blank">The Business Traveller Awards 2024</a> marked a milestone for <a href="https://www.oneworld.com/" target="_blank"><strong>one</strong>world</a>, as the alliance clinched its 12th consecutive <strong>'Best Airline Alliance'</strong> award. This victory during their 25th anniversary year celebrates not just longevity, but continuous innovation in global travel.</p><p class="">The evening was a triumph for <strong>one</strong>world members, with <a href="https://www.oneworld.com/members/qatar-airways" target="_blank">Qatar Airways</a> securing four top awards, including <strong>'Best Long-Haul Airline'</strong> and <strong>'Best Business Class'</strong>. <a href="https://www.oneworld.com/members/british-airways" target="_blank">British Airways</a>, a founding member of the alliance, also shone brightly, winning <strong>'Best Short-Haul Carrier'</strong> and <strong>'Best Frequent Flyer Programme'</strong>, with its iconic Concorde Room at Heathrow Terminal 5 named <strong>'Best Airport Lounge'</strong>.</p><p class="">With 15 member airlines, including <a href="https://www.oneworld.com/members/american-airlines" target="_blank">American Airlines</a>, <a href="https://www.oneworld.com/members/cathay-pacific" target="_blank">Cathay Pacific</a>, <a href="https://www.oneworld.com/members/japan-airlines" target="_blank">Japan Airlines</a>, and <a href="https://www.oneworld.com/members/royal-air-maroc" target="_blank">Royal Air Maroc</a> standing as finalists, <strong>one</strong>world continues to redefine global air travel, proving that excellence is not just about reaching destinations, but about the journey itself.</p>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
