        </figure>
      

    
  


  





  <p class=""><strong>The ULTRAs</strong></p><p class="">Our client Zambia's recognition at <a href="https://www.theultrasawards.com/" target="_blank">The ULTRAs</a> (Ultimate Luxury Travel Related Awards) was a moment of pure pride. The Royal Livingstone Lodge was crowned ‘<strong>Best Hotel in Africa and the Indian Ocean’</strong> – an accolade that celebrates the property's extraordinary blend of elegance and natural wonder. Positioned mere footsteps from the mighty Zambezi River and Victoria Falls, the lodge offers more than just accommodation; it provides a gateway to adventure. From walking safaris in South Luangwa National Park to birdwatching in the Kafue National Park, <a href="https://www.zambiatourism.com/" target="_blank">Zambia</a> represents the ultimate luxury travel experience – where comfort meets unbridled wilderness.&nbsp;</p><p class=""><a href="https://www.rssc.com/" target="_blank">Regent Seven Seas Cruises</a> was recognised as the ‘<strong>Best Luxury Cruise Line’</strong> – a reflection of their commitment to immersive, all-inclusive travel experiences spanning over 550 destinations worldwide. Their unique offering of unlimited complimentary shore excursions represents luxury travel at its most thoughtful.</p>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
        <figure class="
              sqs-block-image-figure
              intrinsic
            "
        >
          
        
        

        
          
            
          
            
                
                
                
                
                
                
                
                <img data-stretch="false" data-image="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/64909d43-0778-41eb-9f4e-f98ae8eab225/A380_RESIDENCE+BEDROOM.jpg" data-image-dimensions="6500x4972" data-image-focal-point="0.5,0.5" alt="" data-load="false" elementtiming="system-image-block" src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/64909d43-0778-41eb-9f4e-f98ae8eab225/A380_RESIDENCE+BEDROOM.jpg?format=1000w" width="6500" height="4972" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, (max-width: 767px) 100vw, 100vw" onload="this.classList.add(&quot;loaded&quot;)" srcset="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/64909d43-0778-41eb-9f4e-f98ae8eab225/A380_RESIDENCE+BEDROOM.jpg?format=100w 100w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/64909d43-0778-41eb-9f4e-f98ae8eab225/A380_RESIDENCE+BEDROOM.jpg?format=300w 300w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/64909d43-0778-41eb-9f4e-f98ae8eab225/A380_RESIDENCE+BEDROOM.jpg?format=500w 500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/64909d43-0778-41eb-9f4e-f98ae8eab225/A380_RESIDENCE+BEDROOM.jpg?format=750w 750w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/64909d43-0778-41eb-9f4e-f98ae8eab225/A380_RESIDENCE+BEDROOM.jpg?format=1000w 1000w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/64909d43-0778-41eb-9f4e-f98ae8eab225/A380_RESIDENCE+BEDROOM.jpg?format=1500w 1500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6595a9416580d436d022fb21/64909d43-0778-41eb-9f4e-f98ae8eab225/A380_RESIDENCE+BEDROOM.jpg?format=2500w 2500w" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-loader="sqs">

            
          
        
          
        

        
      
