  <p class=""><strong>Sunday Times’ Best of All Airlines</strong></p><p class=""><a href="https://www.etihad.com/en-gb/" target="_blank">Etihad Airways </a>also made waves with its extraordinary "The Residence" – a 125-square-foot three-room "penthouse" that redefines first-class travel. Awarded <strong>‘Best of All’</strong> in the Sunday Times, this airborne sanctuary offers everything from personal butlers to champagne and caviar, transforming air travel into a truly memorable journey.</p>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
